== 製作 ==
2017年1月，據報導《[[初戀築夢101|初戀築夢101]]》導演{{link-ko|李勇周 (電影導演)|이용주 (영화 감독)|李勇周}}將執導一部科幻電影，並由[[朴寶劍|朴寶劍]]主角徐福<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2017/01/06/2017010601086.html|script-title=ko:[단독] 박보검 복제인간 된다…영화 '서복'으로 스크린 컴백|publisher=[[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]]|date=2017-01-06|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101200557/https://www.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2017/01/06/2017010601086.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年10月，宣佈[[孔劉|孔劉]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2018/10/11/2018101100702.html|script-title=ko:[공식] 공유, 2년 만에 복귀…이용주 감독 신작 '서복' 출연 확정|publisher=[[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]]|date=2018-10-11|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031050357/https://www.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2018/10/11/2018101100702.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年3月，宣佈[[張英南|張英南]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/news/entertain/view/2019/03/191938/|script-title=ko:장영남, 공유·박보검 주연 `서복` 합류|publisher=每日經濟新聞|date=2019-03-29|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102123216/https://www.mk.co.kr/news/entertain/view/2019/03/191938/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年4月，宣佈[[趙宇鎮|趙宇鎮]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.donga.com/news/Entertainment/article/all/20190403/94864259/1|script-title=ko:공유x박보검x조우진 ‘서복’ 라인업 완성…5월 크랭크인|publisher=[[東亞日報|東亞日報]]|date=2019-04-03|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031145105/https://www.donga.com/news/Entertainment/article/all/20190403/94864259/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2019年5月開始進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2019/04/201720/|script-title=ko:공유X박보검X조우진 ‘서복’ 5월 크랭크인|publisher=每日經濟新聞|date=2019-04-03|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102163913/https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2019/04/201720/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外景拍攝於6月19日至8月初在[[統營市|統營市]]進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20190617_0000682775|script-title=ko:복제인간 영화 '서복', 19일부터 통영시 일원에서 촬영|publisher=[[紐西斯|紐西斯]]|date=2019-06-17|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108081215/https://www.newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20190617_0000682775|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《永生戰》原定於2020年夏季在韓國上映，然而受[[2019冠狀病毒病韓國疫情|2019冠狀病毒病韓國疫情]]影響，電影延期至2020年下半年上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2020060208235742057&DSBA|script-title=ko:[단독]박보검, 해군 지원→8월31일 입대 예정..'원더랜드'·'청춘기록' 촬영中 [종합]|publisher=STARNEWS|date=2020-06-02|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101145412/https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2020060208235742057&DSBA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月，宣佈電影將於2020年12月2日在韓國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/202010/sp20201020191203136680.htm|script-title=ko:[단독] 공유X박보검 '서복', 오는 12월 2일 개봉 확정|publisher=[[韓國日報|韓國日報]]|date=2020-10-20|accessdate=2020-10-28|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101024642/http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/202010/sp20201020191203136680.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月，宣佈電影再度延期上映<ref>{{cite web|author=Erin|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132141|title=哭！今年看不到孔劉與寶劍的《永生戰》了！韓國決定將延期上映|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-12-07|language=zh-hant|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207093028/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132141|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

